---
import SpareCabin from "../../../assets/images/Service/Spare/SpareCabine.webp";
import Aro from "../../../assets/images/Service/Spare/aro.webp";
import bandas from "../../../assets/images/Service/Spare/bandas.webp";
import business from "../../../assets/images/Service/Spare/business.webp";
import mixer from "../../../assets/images/AsphaltPlant/drum4.webp";
import rodillo1 from "../../../assets/images/Service/Spare/rodillo1.webp";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section class="w-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
  <div class="max-w-7xl px-8 mx-auto flex justify-center">
    <Image src={SpareCabin} alt="Spare cabin" class="hero-img lg:w-4/5 rounded-lg" />
  </div>
  <div
    class="max-w-7xl px-8 mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-6"
  >
    <div class="w-full mt-10">
      <h2 class="text-redBg font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl">
          Any time, anywhere
        </h2>
        <p class="text-grisT font-bold text-base md:text-lg">
          We guarantee the fastest response for spare parts. Our dedicated team
          is always ready to support equipment users anywhere, at any time. With
          a specialized spare parts hotline and an efficient logistics system,
          we ensure deliveries in record time so your equipment keeps running
          without delays.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="w-full hidden lg:flex md:w-auto">
      <Image
        src={Aro}
        alt="Ring"
        class="side-img rounded-2xl will-change-transform"
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="max-w-7xl hidden px-8 mx-auto lg:flex justify-center lg:justify-start"
  >
    <Image
      src={bandas}
      alt="Bin unit bands"
      class="fade-img rounded-lg lg:w-3/5 will-change-transform"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="relative flex flex-col lg:hidden">
    <Image
      src={Aro}
      alt="Ring"
      class="rounded-2xl w-[38%] translate-x-[250px] translate-y-2 "
    />

    <Image
      src={bandas}
      alt="Bin unit bands"
      class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-2/3 rounded-lg -translate-x-1 translate-y-2 shadow-lg"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="w-full px-8 md:px-52 text-center py-10 gap-3">
    <h2 class="text-redBg font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl">
      We know this business inside out
    </h2>
    <h3 class="text-grisT font-normal text-lg md:text-2xl">
      With over 30 years of experience, we understand exactly what our clients
      need.
    </h3>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-[#f4f5f6] to-[#393939] w-full h-[150px]">
  </div>
  <div class="bg-grisT w-full text-center flex flex-col gap-2 md:gap-4">
    <h2 class="text-bgBeige font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl">
      Guaranteed quality
    </h2>
    <h2 class="text-bgBeige font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl">Low prices</h2>
    <h2 class="text-bgBeige font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl">
      Short delivery times
    </h2>
  </div>
  <div
    class="bg-grisT w-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center px-8 py-10"
  >
    <div
      class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-10 py-10 max-w-7xl"
    >
      <div class="w-full">
        <Image src={business} alt="TRIASO employees" class="w-3/4 rounded-2xl" />
      </div>
      <div
        class="w-full text-base md:text-lg font-bold text-white h-full flex justify-center items-center"
      >
        <p>
          No other asphalt plant manufacturer in the world produces as many of
          its own components as Triaso. <br />
          This in-house production allows us to offer superior service, industry-leading
          warranties, and direct support from both our Mexican manufacturing facility
          and our U.S. distributor. <br />
          We ship spare parts worldwide to keep your operations running without interruption.
          Every part is backed by certified quality, competitive pricing, and fast
          delivery times.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="w-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
    <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 max-w-[2400px]">
      <div class="w-full pl-4 md:pl-52 font-bold py-10">
        <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-blueMain">TriasoÂ® Inventory</h1><br
        />
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-grisT">
          At Triaso, we prioritize the reliability and performance of your
          equipment by providing high-quality spare parts. Our well-stocked
          warehouse in Durango, Mexico ensures fast and efficient response times
          when you need parts quickly. <br />
          With an advanced cataloging system, we can accurately identify and supply
          the exact components you need. Whether you're looking for standard parts
          or custom solutions, Triaso is ready to deliver.
        </p>
        <div class="w-full">
          <Image src={rodillo1} alt="Triaso Roller" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full flex flex-col">
        <div class="w-full rounded-bl-2xl bg-redBg font-bold">
          <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white py-6 pl-6">
            100% manufactured in-house
          </h1>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full flex justify-end">
          <Image src={mixer} alt="Drum Mixer" class="w-3/5" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    import { initScrollAnimations } from "./scrollAnimationsSpare";

    if (typeof window !== "undefined") {
      window.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
        initScrollAnimations();
      });
    }
  </script>
</section>
